CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 11, 1959, pg. A12 reads: "Cutting Cake - Mr. and Mrs. Raymond Durham cut their recent wedding cake at the home of the bride's sister on Estella St. Elder Tillman performed the ceremony.  The bride is the former Dorothy Reed.  The newlyweds are making their home at 413 Vandalia St. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Raymond Durham and Dorothy Reed Durham, cutting three tiered wedding cake with topper, in home of bride's sister on Estella Street
